# Extension Development

- Build/watch: `pnpm dev` (writes to `dist/`)
- Chrome: `pnpm ext:dev:chrome`
- Edge: `pnpm ext:dev:edge`
- Firefox: `pnpm ext:dev:firefox`
- Safari: use Xcode Safari Web Extension Converter on `dist/`

Hot reload works via `reload.txt` and the background poller in [src/background.ts](mdc:src/background.ts).